                    </div>
                    <span>Out of This Furnace is an engaging story of the struggle of steel mill workers in the early 20th century.  Reading this book felt like going back into time and being able to meet my great-grandparents and see what they went through to establish a better life for me and my family.  Highly recommend this book.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Impressive</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
